Like, we'll keep an open mind, but there's probably nothing here, which I find interesting.

226
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:09,060
Yeah. I mean, I don't know. I have no smoking gun.

227
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:11,660
It just seems quite a curious set of coincidences.

228
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:15,060
You look at what else Jim Simons was really engaged in, right?

229
00:16:15,060 --> 00:16:19,820
He set up the Simons Foundation, which is probably, like, one of the leading private sector sources

230
00:16:19,820 --> 00:16:22,880
of philanthropic funding for fundamental science research.

231
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:29,400
And his, you know, guy running his private research foundation in fundamental physics

232
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:31,680
gets tapped to run the UAP working group for NASA.

233
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:32,180
Yeah.

234
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:39,180
Weinstein is on Rogan actively speculating that this is housing a sort of secret physics program

235
00:16:39,180 --> 00:16:42,440
involving all the top differential geometers in the U.S.

236
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:44,060
What do you think, Matthew?

237
00:16:44,560 --> 00:16:47,520
I mean, if such a thing were to exist, that's exactly where it would exist.

238
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:48,220
Yeah.

239
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:51,760
And who knows? Maybe Spurgle has nothing to do with UFOs.

240
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:56,720
Maybe the Wall Street Journal genuinely believes the bullshit about EMPs they're promoting.

241
00:16:56,720 --> 00:17:01,920
But it's just so weird to me that they've been working on a UFO-related story for months

242
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:09,040
and neglected to mention that a cabinet member was involved in a UFO-related op-ed proposal

243
00:17:09,040 --> 00:17:10,740
that they received last year.

244
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:18,160
So bad faith acting, incompetence, I'll let you decide.

245
00:17:18,300 --> 00:17:19,820
I'll just end on this note.

246
00:17:19,820 --> 00:17:27,000
If UFOs are all just some fake, multi-decade-long hazing ritual, then nobody should have any issue

247
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:29,700
