248
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:34,220
Who cares if we have civilian oversight over programs that don't exist?

249
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:37,940
And hopefully when the UAP Disclosure Act goes up for vote again,

250
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:41,560
Sean Kirkpatrick won't lobby against it like he did last time.

251
00:17:41,780 --> 00:17:46,940
So on that note, I'm linking a petition below that you will hopefully all sign in support

252
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,560
