257
00:18:05,620 --> 00:18:07,940
So please, Wall Street Journal, do better next time.

258
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:09,520
We need better debunkers.

259
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:11,080
I'm not anti-debunking.

260
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:14,400
There's plenty of bullshit in UFO World, a lot of which I cover.

261
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:17,300
I'm just anti-bad, lazy debunking.

262
00:18:17,460 --> 00:18:22,380
And if Joel Schechtman or Sean Kirkpatrick or Susan Goff or any of these people want to come

263
00:18:22,380 --> 00:18:27,920
